                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-278016573" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="278016573">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/seabaikal/">贝加尔海</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar30 rating" title="还行"></span>
                    <span>2010-08-03</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">具体在三星和四星之间，贴书评了——虽然还是把学术书的评论写的偏文艺了~~</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="247424258">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-247424258" class="vote-count">0</span>
