  <ul class="comments by_rank" >
      
      <li class="ctsh clearfix" data-cid="33698757">
        <div class="ilst">
          <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/3375154/"><img src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u3375154-4.jpg" alt="苏一" class="" /></a>
        </div>
        <div class="con">
          <div class="nlst">
            <h3>
              <div class="note-toggle rr">
                <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/33698757/" class="note-unfolder">展开</a>
                <a href="javascript:void(0);" class="note-folder">收起</a>
              </div>
              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/33698757/" class="">第162页</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/3375154/" class=" " title="苏一">苏一</a>
                (思想的西西弗斯，行动的堂吉诃德)
              
                <span class="allstar40" title="推荐"></span>
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="33698757">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">戒、定、慧</span>
                <p class="pl">
